title: Weekly Move-in Special
posting_body: We're 8 minutes from the Square in Downtown Georgetown.
******NEW MANAGMENT******
There is several shopping, eating, grocery and public transportation options within a five-minute driving distance of the property.
All of our suites include:
· ALL UTILITIES
· Full size refrigerator
· Microwave
· Two Burner Stove
· Free WIFI
· Flat Screen TVs with 50 cable channels
Pets are welcome!
We have a fitness center on site.
***Please note room totals do not include tax***
**Limited to first time guests.
Must mention offer at time of reservation.
**Price of $364.00 plus tax for the week month.
Prices subject to change.
*Pets are always welcome at Woodspring Suites.
A maximum of two pets are allowed in each suite.
A $5 (+ tax) per week, per pet non-refundable cleaning fee for the first month.
This fee is to cover the cost of cleaning and fumigating guest room.
Height and length restrictions apply pets can be no longer than 36 inches and no taller than 36 inches.
Larger, or more than two pets requires property manager's approval.
All rates are due in full at time of check -in.
